          "_name": "header9",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"header9\" group=\"Headers\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n                    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"9\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"9\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Arrow\" name=\"showArrow\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitle\" name=\"showSubTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#000000\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Background Video\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.2\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-column mbr-white col-md-8\">\n            <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title align-left mbr-bold pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">STORY OF A BRAND'S</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span>BIRTH</h1>\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle align-left mbr-light pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubTitle\"><div><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">—&nbsp;</span><br></div><div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\">Project Owners:</span></div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">Gaj International Publications</span></b></span></div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><b>Gaj Innovation Center</b></span></div><div><br></div></div><div><div><br></div><div>—</div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-size: 1.2rem;\">My Solution:\n</span></div><div><b style=\"font-style: normal; font-size: 1.2rem;\">UX Design Direction</b></div></div><div><div><b style=\"font-style: normal; font-size: 1.2rem;\">User Test</b></div></div><div><div><b style=\"font-style: normal; font-size: 1.2rem;\">Concept Logos<br></b><br></div><br><div><br>—<br><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\">Descriptions:</span></div></div></div></h3>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text align-left pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><br><b>About Gajino:</b><b><br></b><br>Gajino is a mobile application for biggest educational international publications in Iran.<br>The persona of this service are students (kids and teenagers).<br><br>My role in this project was the design lead, I create a design team with UX assistant (intern) and UI/UX designer. We made two different designs:<br>1st design: developed by the product team before our start (design team).<br>2nd version: after our results from researches, accessibility roles for this special persona and results from the same type of user tests like usability. from our results; navigation (user journey), mental model, UI and design strategy basically changed on this version.<br>Also, I working personally on logo sign of this service.<br><br></p>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><a class=\"btn btn-md btn-white-outline\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=ir.gaj.gajino&hl=en\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"mbri-play mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\" style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204);\"></span>Android App</a>\n                <a class=\"btn btn-md btn-white-outline\" href=\"https://sibapp.com/applications/gajino-1\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"mbrib-apple mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\" style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204);\"></span>iOS App</a> <a class=\"btn btn-md btn-white-outline\" href=\"https://sibapp.com/applications/gajino-1\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"mbri-globe-2 mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\" style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204);\"></span>Website</a></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-if=\"showArrow\" class=\"mbr-arrow hidden-sm-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <a href=\"#next\">\n            <i class=\"mbri-down mbr-iconfont\"></i>\n        </a>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_anchor": "header9-g3",
