      "settings": {
        "meta_descr": "Pishkhan is a service that a large number of magazines, newspapers, News and Web sites and publications are present in digital publishing large family and in this service, in per issue of publications excerpts of content and images send to their users base on MMS. ",
        "title": "MTN PISHKHAN  —  BMDX",
