          },
          "_name": "header9",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"header9\" group=\"Headers\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n                    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"9\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"9\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Arrow\" name=\"showArrow\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitle\" name=\"showSubTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#000000\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Background Video\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.2\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-column mbr-white col-md-8\">\n            <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title align-left mbr-bold pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">STORY OF A BRAND'S</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span>BIRTH</h1>\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle align-left mbr-light pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubTitle\"><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">—&nbsp;</span><br></span></div><div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\">Project Owners:</span></div><div><b style=\"font-style: normal;\">Cheragh Job Portal System&nbsp;</b></div></div><div><div><b style=\"font-style: normal;\">Toucan Maham Fan</b></div></div><div><div><b style=\"font-style: normal;\">Mobodid</b></div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><br></span></div></div><div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><br></span></div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\">—</span></div><div><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: normal;\">My Solution:\n</span></div><div><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: normal;\">Design Direction [Website, Mobile Application]</b></div></div><div><div><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: normal;\">User Experience Design</b></div></div><div><div><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: normal;\">User Interface Design</b></div></div><div><div><b style=\"font-size: 1.2rem; font-style: normal;\">Branding [Brand Booklet]</b><br></div><br><div><br>—<br><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\">Descriptions:</span></div></div></div></h3>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text align-left pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><br><b>About Cheragh:</b><b><br></b><br>“Cheragh” &nbsp;(It means Light in Persian) &nbsp;is a startup at early stages that connects candidates who are looking for a job with the opportunities that suit them best. It also offers a wide variety of educational contents and personality tests.<br>Cheragh is a job board used by employers to advertise their job vacancies to job seekers. Job seekers can use Cheragh to search for new job opportunities in their area and profession. They can build their resume online very easily on Cheragh and apply for job opportunities.\n<br>Cheragh includes all job categories and fields. Cheragh opportunities are update every day and job seekers with various levels of skills can find their right fit job opportunities and apply for them.\n<br>Cheragh also has Online Learning courses based on VOD, job seekers can participate in this courses and improve their abilities to be more skillful to increase their chance for getting better job opportunities.<br><br></p>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><a class=\"btn btn-md btn-white-outline\" href=\"https://xd.adobe.com/view/2fe50675-c307-439b-60a3-47287e8e5911-59d4/?fullscreen\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"mbri-mobile mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\" style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204);\"></span>Hi-Fi Prototype<br></a>\n                <a class=\"btn btn-md btn-white-outline\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.toucan.cheragh\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"mbri-play mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\" style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204);\"></span>Android App</a>  <a class=\"btn btn-md btn-white-outline\" href=\"https://www.cheragh.com/\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"mbri-globe-2 mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\" style=\"color: rgb(204, 204, 204);\"></span>Website</a></div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-if=\"showArrow\" class=\"mbr-arrow hidden-sm-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <a href=\"#next\">\n            <i class=\"mbri-down mbr-iconfont\"></i>\n        </a>\n    </div>\n</section>",
